oidal obscuration and off-plane\nscattering, implying that the model can be extended to include at least some\nhigh-luminosity AGNs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 3 Oct 2004 17:02:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 19 Nov 2004 16:40:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
